<index.html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Loan Calculators</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #f4f7fb, #e9f0fa);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .container {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      width: 1000px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 160px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #003366;
    }
    .calculator {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: #fafafa;
      text-align: left;
      position: relative;
    }
    .calculator h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    label {
      display: block;
      margin: 8px 0 4px;
    }
    input, select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
    select.small {
      width: auto;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }
    button {
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: #007bff;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    button:hover {
      background: #0056b3;
    }
    .remove-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      background: #dc3545;
    }
    .remove-btn:hover {
      background: #a71d2a;
    }
    .summary-btn {
      margin-left: 10px;
      background: #28a745;
    }
    .summary-btn.remove {
      background: #ffc107;
      color: #000;
    }
    .mode-btn {
      margin-left: 10px;
      background: #6f42c1;
    }
    .results {
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: #eef2f7;
    }
    .summary {
      border: 2px solid #007bff;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #f9fbff;
      text-align: left;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="data:image/jpg;base64," alt="Company Logo" class="logo">


    <h1>Loan Calculators</h1>

    <div id="calculators"></div>
    <button onclick="addCalculator()">➕ Add Calculator</button>

    <div class="summary">
      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <div id="summaryContent">No calculators included yet.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    let calcCount = 0;
    let includedCalcs = {};
    let modes = {}; // Track mode per calculator

    // ---- EasyLaw Malaysia Formulas ----
    function calcStampDutyMOT(price) {
      let duty = 0;
      if (price > 1000000) { duty += (price - 1000000) * 0.04; price = 1000000; }
      if (price > 500000) { duty += (price - 500000) * 0.03; price = 500000; }
      if (price > 100000) { duty += (price - 100000) * 0.02; price = 100000; }
      if (price > 0) duty += price * 0.01;
      return duty;
    }
    function calcStampDutyLoan(loan) {
      return loan * 0.005;
    }
    function calcLegalFees(amount) {
      let fee = 0;
      if (amount > 5000000) { fee += (amount - 5000000) * 0.005; amount = 5000000; }
      if (amount > 3000000) { fee += (amount - 3000000) * 0.006; amount = 3000000; }
      if (amount > 1000000) { fee += (amount - 1000000) * 0.007; amount = 1000000; }
      if (amount > 500000) { fee += (amount - 500000) * 0.008; amount = 500000; }
      if (amount > 0) fee += amount * 0.01;
      return fee;
    }

    function addCalculator() {
      calcCount++;
      modes[calcCount] = "loan"; // default mode = by loan size
      const container = document.getElementById("calculators");
      const calcDiv = document.createElement("div");
      calcDiv.className = "calculator";
      calcDiv.id = "calc" + calcCount;

      calcDiv.innerHTML = `
        <button class="remove-btn" onclick="removeCalculator(${calcCount})">✖</button>
        <h2>Calculator ${calcCount}</h2>
        <label>Calculator Title</label>
        <input type="text" id="title${calcCount}" placeholder="Type a title (e.g. P2P Loan)">
        
        <label>Calculator Type</label>
        <select id="type${calcCount}" class="small" onchange="renderInputs(${calcCount})">
          <option value="P2P">P2P</option>
          <option value="Bank Loan">Bank Loan</option>
          <option value="Mortgage">Mortgage</option>
        </select>
        <button class="mode-btn" onclick="toggleMode(${calcCount})">Switch to Monthly Mode</button>
        <div id="inputs${calcCount}"></div>
        <button onclick="calculate(${calcCount})">Calculate</button>
        <button id="summaryBtn${calcCount}" class="summary-btn" onclick="toggleSummary(${calcCount})">Add to Summary</button>
        <div class="results" id="results${calcCount}"></div>
      `;
      container.appendChild(calcDiv);
      renderInputs(calcCount);
    }

    function removeCalculator(id) {
      document.getElementById("calc" + id).remove();
      delete includedCalcs[id];
      delete modes[id];
      updateGlobalSummary();
    }

    function toggleMode(id) {
      modes[id] = modes[id] === "loan" ? "monthly" : "loan";
      const btn = document.querySelector(`#calc${id} .mode-btn`);
      btn.textContent = modes[id] === "loan" ? "Switch to Monthly Mode" : "Switch to Loan Size Mode";
      renderInputs(id);
    }

    function renderInputs(id) {
      const type = document.getElementById("type" + id).value;
      const mode = modes[id];
      let inputsHTML = "";

      if (type === "Mortgage") {
        if (mode === "loan") {
          inputsHTML = `
            <label>SNP Price (RM)</label>
            <input type="number" id="snp${id}">
            <label>Loan Size (RM)</label>
            <input type="number" id="loan${id}">
          `;
        } else {
          inputsHTML = `
            <label>SNP Price (RM)</label>
            <input type="number" id="snp${id}">
            <label>Monthly Payment (RM)</label>
            <input type="number" id="monthly${id}">
          `;
        }
        inputsHTML += `
          <label>Interest Rate (%)</label>
          <input type="number" id="rate${id}">
          <label>Tenure (Years)</label>
          <input type="number" id="tenure${id}">
          <label>Service Fees (%)</label>
          <input type="number" id="fees${id}">
          <label>Cash Back Mode</label>
          <select id="cashbackMode${id}">
            <option value="none">None</option>
            <option value="percent">By % of SNP</option>
            <option value="manual">Manual RM</option>
          </select>
          <input type="number" id="cashback${id}" placeholder="Enter % or RM">
        `;
      } else {
        if (mode === "loan") {
          inputsHTML = `
            <label>Loan Size (RM)</label>
            <input type="number" id="loan${id}">
          `;
        } else {
          inputsHTML = `
            <label>Monthly Payment (RM)</label>
            <input type="number" id="monthly${id}">
          `;
        }
        inputsHTML += `
          <label>Interest Rate (%)</label>
          <input type="number" id="rate${id}">
          <label>Tenure (Years)</label>
          <input type="number" id="tenure${id}">
          <label>Service Fees (%)</label>
          <input type="number" id="fees${id}">
        `;
      }
      document.getElementById("inputs" + id).innerHTML = inputsHTML;
    }

    function calculate(id) {
      const type = document.getElementById("type" + id).value;
      const mode = modes[id];
      const title = document.getElementById("title" + id).value || type;
      const rate = parseFloat(document.getElementById("rate" + id)?.value) || 0;
      const tenure = parseFloat(document.getElementById("tenure" + id)?.value) || 0;
      const fees = parseFloat(document.getElementById("fees" + id)?.value) || 0;

      let loan = 0, monthly = 0, serviceFee = 0, cashOnHand = 0;

      if (type === "Mortgage") {
        const snp = parseFloat(document.getElementById("snp" + id)?.value) || 0;
        const n = tenure * 12;
        const monthlyRate = rate / 100 / 12;

        if (mode === "loan") {
          loan = parseFloat(document.getElementById("loan" + id)?.value) || 0;
          monthly = loan * monthlyRate / (1 - Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, -n));
        } else {
          monthly = parseFloat(document.getElementById("monthly" + id)?.value) || 0;
          loan = monthly * (1 - Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, -n)) / monthlyRate;
        }

        serviceFee = loan * (fees / 100);

        const cbMode = document.getElementById("cashbackMode" + id).value;
        const cbValue = parseFloat(document.getElementById("cashback" + id)?.value) || 0;
        let cashback = 0;
        if (cbMode === "percent") cashback = snp * (cbValue / 100);
        if (cbMode === "manual") cashback = cbValue;

        const mot = calcStampDutyMOT(snp);
        const loanStamp = calcStampDutyLoan(loan);
        const legalSNP = calcLegalFees(snp);
        const legalLoan = calcLegalFees(loan);
        const totalExpenses = mot + loanStamp + legalSNP + legalLoan;

        document.getElementById("results" + id).innerHTML = `
          <strong>${title}</strong><br>
          Loan Size: RM ${loan.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
          SNP Price: RM ${snp.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Interest Rate: ${rate}%<br>
          Tenure: ${tenure} years<br>
          Service Fee: RM ${serviceFee.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Monthly Payment: RM ${monthly.toLocaleString(undefined, {maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
          Cashback: RM ${cashback.toLocaleString()}<br><br>
          <u>Estimated Expenses (not included in total fees)</u><br>
          MOT Stamp Duty: RM ${mot.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Loan Stamp Duty: RM ${loanStamp.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Legal Fees (SNP): RM ${legalSNP.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Legal Fees (Loan): RM ${legalLoan.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Total Estimated Expenses: RM ${totalExpenses.toLocaleString()}</strong><br>
          Remark: Effective Rate Calculation. Other misc. fees may apply.
        `;
      } else {
        const n = tenure * 12;
        if (mode === "loan") {
          loan = parseFloat(document.getElementById("loan" + id)?.value) || 0;
          monthly = (loan * (1 + (rate / 100) * tenure)) / (tenure * 12);
        } else {
          monthly = parseFloat(document.getElementById("monthly" + id)?.value) || 0;
          loan = monthly * n / (1 + (rate / 100) * tenure);
        }
        serviceFee = loan * (fees / 100);

        let bankDeduction = 0;
        if (type === "P2P") {
          const platformFee = loan * (0.015 * tenure);
          bankDeduction = platformFee + monthly;
          cashOnHand = loan - serviceFee - platformFee - monthly;
        } else if (type === "Bank Loan") {
          bankDeduction = loan * 0.015;
          cashOnHand = loan - serviceFee - bankDeduction;
        }

        document.getElementById("results" + id).innerHTML = `
          <strong>${title}</strong><br>
          Loan Size: RM ${loan.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
          Interest Rate: ${rate}%<br>
          Tenure: ${tenure} years<br>
          Service Fee: RM ${serviceFee.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Monthly Payment: RM ${monthly.toLocaleString(undefined, {maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
          Cash on Hand: RM ${cashOnHand.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Bank Deduction (estimated): RM ${bankDeduction.toLocaleString()}<br>
          Remark: Flat Rate Calculation
        `;
      }
    }

    function toggleSummary(id) {
      const btn = document.getElementById("summaryBtn" + id);
      if (includedCalcs[id]) {
        delete includedCalcs[id];
        btn.textContent = "Add to Summary";
        btn.classList.remove("remove");
      } else {
        calculate(id); // ensure values are fresh
        const type = document.getElementById("type" + id).value;
        const title = document.getElementById("title" + id).value || type;
        const loan = parseFloat(document.getElementById("loan" + id)?.value) || 0;
        const monthly = parseFloat(document.getElementById("monthly" + id)?.value) || 0;
        const serviceFee = parseFloat(document.getElementById("fees" + id)?.value) / 100 * loan || 0;
        let cashback = 0, expenses = 0, cashOnHand = 0;
        if (type === "Mortgage") {
          cashback = parseFloat(document.getElementById("cashback" + id)?.value) || 0;
          expenses = calcStampDutyMOT(loan) + calcStampDutyLoan(loan) + calcLegalFees(loan);
        } else {
          cashOnHand = loan - serviceFee;
        }
        includedCalcs[id] = { title, loan, serviceFee, monthly, cashback, cashOnHand, expenses, type };
        btn.textContent = "Remove from Summary";
        btn.classList.add("remove");
      }
      updateGlobalSummary();
    }

    function updateGlobalSummary() {
      let totalLoan = 0, totalFees = 0, totalCash = 0, totalExpenses = 0, totalMonthly = 0;
      let listItems = "";

      for (let id in includedCalcs) {
        const c = includedCalcs[id];
        totalLoan += c.loan;
        totalFees += c.serviceFee;
        totalMonthly += c.monthly;
        if (c.type === "Mortgage") {
          totalCash += c.cashback;
          totalExpenses += c.expenses;
        } else {
          totalCash += c.cashOnHand;
        }
        listItems += `<li><strong>${c.title}</strong> → Loan Size: RM ${c.loan.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}, Monthly: RM ${c.monthly.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}</li>`;
      }

      if (listItems === "") {
        document.getElementById("summaryContent").innerHTML = "No calculators included yet.";
        return;
      }

      document.getElementById("summaryContent").innerHTML = `
        <strong>Total Loan Size:</strong> RM ${totalLoan.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
        <strong>Total Service Fees:</strong> RM ${totalFees.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
        <strong>Total Monthly Payment:</strong> RM ${totalMonthly.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
        <strong>Total Cash (P2P + Bank Loan / Cashback for Mortgage):</strong> RM ${totalCash.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
        <strong>Total Mortgage Expenses:</strong> RM ${totalExpenses.toLocaleString(undefined,{maximumFractionDigits:2})}<br>
        <br><u>Details by Calculator:</u>
        <ul>${listItems}</ul>
      `;
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
